title: shrI rAmacandruniki
sahitya:
shrI rAmacandruniki sObanE mA rAmamUrtiki vaibhavamE


anupallavi

  vIrAdi dInuniki dinamaNI vamshuniki mA rAmamUrtiki sObanam sEyavE


caraNam    shrI ramacandruniki vaibhavam sEyavE shrI rAmacanduniki
sObanamE divya vaibhavamE nitya kalyANamE sObanamE vaibhavamE
